setStatus

public void setStatus(java.lang.String string,
                      int i)
Sets the status of the splash window based on the given arguments.

Parameters:
string - The message to be displayed above the progress bar.
i - The percent completion to be displayed within the progress bar. If i > maximum or i < minimum, then the indeterminate state will be displayed (cylon status).
